    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an affordable price, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers who want solid everyday utility without a big upfront cost. It shows its age, but it still offers real value with a straightforward driving experience and the kind of honest character many budget-conscious shoppers appreciate. A smart option for commuting, a second vehicle, or a project-minded owner looking for an inexpensive entry point.",
