    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Reliable, affordable, and ready for its next owner. This is a great budget-friendly car for someone who wants simple transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it starts, runs, and offers a solid foundation for a daily driver, backup vehicle, or project. If you\u2019re looking for honest value and a car that can still do the job, this one is worth a look.",
