    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s the perfect canvas for someone who appreciates a machine with stories to tell\u2014whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly daily, a creative project, or a fun runaround with vintage grit and charm. Distinctive presence, memorable lines, and plenty of potential make this one an easy choice for the buyer who sees opportunity where others just see age.",
