      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age cosmetically and may need some attention, but it presents a solid opportunity for a handy buyer, commuter, or anyone seeking inexpensive wheels without overpaying. Priced to reflect its condition and deliver strong value.",
